    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can't choose what game to play? Well this game is the game for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>Games for the Table</u> is a game with many games inside So far, the game contains a handful of games: checkers, chess, a unique fusion of checkers and chess, and a version of the well-know game, Crazy Eights, in development currently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Week after week, updates will be posted to the game, either adding new games to play or updating the games already present. Though I am a full-time employee and attend school full time also, I will try my best to update the game with more content and fixes as fast as possible!</p>",
